'''Neva Transport''' was a transport company that operated in the [[Brak sector/Legends|Brak sector]]. It was affiliated with the [[Nalmar Family|Nalmar crime family]]. [[Elana Nalmar]] operated the [[Light freighter/Legends|light freighter]] ''[[Early Riser]]'' which was registered to Neva Transport.

